#originalTopic=what-do-guns-mean-to-americans
An armed populace has the ability to check the power of government. The first thing dictators do when they take over a nation is disarm the populace to make them easier to control. Government can call the restrictions they want to put on us safety reasons if they want to, but it's really about safety for them, not for us.